Package: extractionengine
Type: Package
Title: Auditable Execution of Study Variable Definitions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Francesco",
      family = "Monti",
      email = "58150610+FrancescoMonti-source@users.noreply.github.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Executes explicit operational definitions of study variables over
    prepared EDSAN views. It keeps values, source coverage, evidence, and
    execution provenance together so that each result can be audited. Clinical
    and scientific definitions remain the researcher's responsibility.
